Package uk.co.strangeskies.scripting

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InvocableBase
    A partial implementation of Invocable which implements InvocableBase.getInterface(Class) and InvocableBase.getInterface(Object, Class) by proxying the requested class and delegating invocations to Invocable.invokeFunction(String, Object...) and Invocable.invokeMethod(Object, String, Object...) respectively.
